setSimRect

  • setSimRect(simRect: DoubleRect): void
    • Defined in davinci-newton/view/LabView.ts:80

    Sets the bounding rectangle for this LabView, ensures this rectangle is visible, and turns off auto-scaling. The result is to generate a new CoordMap for this SimView so that the simulation rectangle maps to the current screen rectangle.

    Parameters

      the bounding rectangle for this LabView in simulation coordinates.
